GMapPresentation is a simple presentation UI utilizing Google Maps. 

Using GMapPresentation you can place a series of slides at a variety of places around globe.  As you jump from slide to slide, the map will fly to the location of the next slide.

Supports keyboard navigation from slide to slide including up-down, left-right, page-up-page-down, and spacebar.

Supports jumping between slides by clicking the slide title in the right-hand pane. 

To use:
Open index.html and find YOUR_KEY_HERE and replace it with your Google Maps key.

To change slide data:
Open slides.js, and modify as needed. 